345
00:27:03,186 --> 00:27:04,888
We wanted to get Oharlie Stiffle,

346
00:27:04,955 --> 00:27:07,891
- but we ended up getting Oharlie...
- Bratley.

347
00:27:07,958 --> 00:27:09,526
Oharlie Bratley.

348
00:27:09,560 --> 00:27:13,463
Wait a minute, Bratley? Is...?
Is your mother Terri Bratley,

349
00:27:13,530 --> 00:27:16,300
