in the Ocean Orest development.

364
00:27:56,473 --> 00:27:58,242
Anyway, I...

365
00:28:08,318 --> 00:28:12,089
- This is Terri Bratley...
- Hi, I'm Jerri Falls...

366
00:28:23,567 --> 00:28:25,636
- Hello?
- Dean?

367
00:28:25,702 --> 00:28:28,038
Jesus. Oan't you guys
just leave me alone?

368
00:28:28,105 --> 00:28:31,241
- I'd love to, but I can't.
