381
00:28:59,403 --> 00:29:02,739
Oharlie! Oharlie!

382
00:29:02,806 --> 00:29:05,142
Billy, get off of him.

383
00:29:05,209 --> 00:29:07,544
Oharlie, come here.

384
00:29:17,955 --> 00:29:20,090
- Hello?
- Who is this?

385
00:29:20,157 --> 00:29:22,626
