with me again, or is this real?

393
00:29:44,648 --> 00:29:47,384
No, I think this is pretty real.

394
00:30:05,969 --> 00:30:08,205
- Yes?
- Hi. Is Oharlie here?

395
00:30:08,272 --> 00:30:10,507
